oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pee Wee King and Redd Stewart: Larger Image
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Collins Sisters; Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency; King, Pee Wee, 1914-2000; Leonard, Jack; Offset printing; Stewart, Redd;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising Pee Wee King and his band with Redd Stewart, Jack Leonard, the Collins Sisters, the New Golden West Cowboys, Jim Vest, Russ Caswell, and others, available through the Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency. The negatives feature photographs of Pee Wee King, Redd Stewart, Jack Leonard, and the Collins Sisters and would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
